{"word":"Mareshah","slug":"mareshah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Mareshah</b> <a href=\"#/H4762\">H4762</a> <br/> 1. A city of Judah:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=44'>Jos 15:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=8'>2Ch 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=14&verse=10'>2Ch 14:10</a> <br/> - Birthplace of Eliezer the prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=37'>2Ch 20:37</a> <br/> - Prophecy concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=15'>Mic 1:15</a> <br/> 2. Father of Hebron<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=2&verse=42'>1Ch 2:42</a><br/> 3. A son of, or possibly a city founded by Laadah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=21'>1Ch 4:21</a>"}]}